{"tid":3126,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴控走資】傳中國擬嚴控大宗對外投資交易","createTime":"2016-11-26T05:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T16:10:54.000Z","uid":3467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6546d530440a08ba62561b8548570ebb488869a","tid":3126,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"支那經濟爆升系列<br />\n<br />\n中國計劃進一步控制資本流走，《華爾街日報》引述消息人士透露，國務院即將公司一系列措施，對企業海外交易將從嚴控制。受到嚴控的交易包括10億美元以上的大宗房地產交易；100億美元以上的對外投資項目以及10億以上非主業大額對外投資。<br />\n<br />\n有關新措施預計實施至明年9月底，通過一系列臨時工具於明年高層換屆前穩定資本外流。根據目前規定，上述交易只要向監管機構登記備案，無需經過任何審批程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161126&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55968120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161126%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55968120&d=EFbZueceQ7Qqbt7oTrAnXsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=c796a4ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161126%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55968120&h=b473a5ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161126&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55968120</a><br />\n【嚴控走資】傳中國擬嚴控大宗對外投資交易"},{"pid":"675031335021435c7e81b8abc4d033c778f5ee00","tid":3126,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"內地傳出廣州、南京由本月25日起至30日暫停發放個人房貸，包括所有子產品。消息指，是收到人行要求銀行對其個人住房貸款新增餘額進行控制，請銀行站在政治高度及可持續發展的角度，多措並舉，認真貫徹落實監管部門及總行的決策部署。<br />\n<br />\n然而，暫時在人行官網及微博，以至人行廣州分行及南京分行的官網均未見到相關消息發佈。此前，人行調查統計司司長阮健弘曾指，今年首9個月個人住房貸款新增3.63萬億元，較去年同期多增1.8萬億元。當中9月份個人住房貸款新增4759億元，按年多增2055億元，增長較快主因是今年以來全國房地產市場走勢分化，部分一、二線城市房地產成交活躍。而首3季個人住房貸款增量佔全部貸款增量的35.7%，<br />\n<br />\n另外，住建部今日公佈了30家違法違規房地產中介機構名單，該部指在本月25日，召開了規範房地產中介行為持續整頓市場秩序電視電話會議，主要因中介行業違法違規問題仍較為突出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161125&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55966349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161125%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55966349&d=EFbZueceQ7Qqbt7oTrAnXsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b495f53c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161125%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55966349&h=6e2173c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161125&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55966349</a><br />\n【規模太大】傳廣州、南京暫停個人房貸至月底"},{"pid":"03c7059b826b780c6fd654ea42b77d740da2794b","tid":3126,"uid":8347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce23747aad778d037ce7b47914ac6135ad24407","tid":3126,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"爆爆爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0567920c7d07ccd8c7bb2951bba619a673f82a","tid":3126,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cf3cc5760e4c128ddef3d1bbc1acbf67e05ced","tid":3126,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"銀芽～～～～～～"},{"pid":"85df474769c1583f1ec20fd837b5769a843e4ea1","tid":3126,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"香港d寫字樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb2a0870332f2ae9bc517d5bb78a14be7f00d0f","tid":3126,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"其實由舊年年尾開始逐步收緊，都玩左成年，而家好明顯係止唔到瀉"},{"pid":"c5835f01936d06d2fa93c4a17d682d7989c53402","tid":3126,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s